
Privacy Policy



tinyTerm2 does not collect any user data, except when logs are reqeusted for bug reports, 

debug logs are used for trouble shooting purpose only, data is never shared with external 

parties unless explicitly requested by the user.



tinyTerm2 is hosted on GitHub and Microsoft/Apple app stores, use of those sites governed

by privacy policy of each site, author of tinyTerm2 does not track or store data of users 

except to fulfill the user requested actions, or to aid in fixing technical problems.

 
